---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Damian Zakrzewski | Bioinformatics">
	<main class="mt-4">
		<!-- Profilowe -->
		<img 
	      		src="/profilowe.jpg"
			alt="Damian Zakrzewski"
			class="w-24 h-24 sm:w-32 sm:h-32 rounded-full object-cover shadow-sm border border-slate-200 mb-8"
		/>
		<!-- Zmieniony, punktowy nagłówek -->
		<h1 class="font-['Cormorant_Garamond'] italic text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-wide leading-tight">
			Bioinformatics Student. Web Developer. Research Assistant.
		</h1>
		
		<!-- Nowy opis o Tobie -->
		<div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm sm:text-base space-y-6 mb-12">
			<p>
				I am a 6th-semester bioinformatics student at Poznań University of Technology. My primary research interests revolve around <strong>RNA folding and structural biology</strong>, with a specific focus on the behavior of <strong>extended non-canonical helices</strong>.
			</p>
			<p>
				I thrive at the intersection of computer science and biology, actively working to bridge the gap between computational predictions and physical reality. To achieve this, I am dedicated to developing my skills not only in dry-lab informatics and software development but also by embracing the rigorous methodologies and hands-on environment of wet-lab research.
			</p>
			<p>
				Beyond my core academic research, I serve as an IT Administrator for the <strong>Solar Dynamics PUT</strong> science club, where I manage technical infrastructure and support interdisciplinary engineering initiatives.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Sekcja z obecnymi projektami, którą mieliśmy już wcześniej -->
		<h2 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-slate-400 mb-6">Current Focus</h2>
		
		<ul class="space-y-6 text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 mb-12">
			<li class="relative pl-4 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:w-1 before:h-1 before:bg-slate-300 before:rounded-full">
				<strong>RNA Structure Analysis:</strong> Lead author of the RNABridge web application under the supervision of Prof. M. Antczak and Prof. T. Żok <em>(Publication in preparation, pre-submission to JMB)</em>.
			</li>
			<li class="relative pl-4 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:w-1 before:h-1 before:bg-slate-300 before:rounded-full">
				<strong>Materials Chemistry:</strong> Synthesizing and modifying Metal-Organic Frameworks (TMU-16 and TMU-16 NH₂) at Adam Mickiewicz University in collaboration with Prof. J. Gościańska and Dr. A. Ejsmont.
			</li>
			<li class="relative pl-4 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-2 before:w-1 before:h-1 before:bg-slate-300 before:rounded-full">
				<strong>Chemical Technology:</strong> Collaborationg with Dr. Adam Grzywaczyk at the PUT Faculty of Chemical Technology on research concerning the toxicity of pharmaceuticals. 
			</li>
		</ul>
<!-- Link do CV -->
		<div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-900/5">
			<a 
				href="/CV_Damian_Zakrzewski.pdf" 
				target="_blank" 
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-900 hover:text-slate-500 transition-colors"
			>
				View Curriculum Vitae
				<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1 group-hover:-translate-y-1">
					<path d="M7 7h10v10"/>
					<path d="M7 17 17 7"/>
				</svg>
			</a>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
